{"tid":389303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"icloud drive 問題","createTime":"2017-09-06T06:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T13:41:06.000Z","uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73e1adaee0a19878a4838a39687b607f64a83c5f","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"有無人知點解我個 icloud drive入面係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/145343_8ded0772ff2ee4da1e41866945d81c9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F145343_8ded0772ff2ee4da1e41866945d81c9b.jpg&h=0d87ddd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我設定入空係有開到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/145402_d70d24b0418f77b4badbd4400906e137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F145402_d70d24b0418f77b4badbd4400906e137.jpg&h=09c4f380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb4f61789a7d6825cce151af2ddc49a49a4fe8","tid":389303,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚"},{"pid":"c0ecca113e968ffda230120440cd35e58aec3071","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下點先可以個別回復一個app既date？<br />\n因為我唔小心del左個i safe pro, 重裝之後無哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d野仲係iclould度 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc1bd67a960f92dde98a2e690f0167e7bfd6672","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f96411db26e761802585f1b6e3f05e6a89f8415","tid":389303,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下點先可以個別回復一個app既date？<br />\n因為我唔小心del左個i safe pro, 重裝之後無哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d野仲係iclould度 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣冇得搞<br />\nicloud drive isafe呢個位唔係for你咁用<br />\n佢唔係用嚟記app data, 應該for放文件之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你平時有冇做icloud backup<br />\n成部嘢restore一次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a3e1c6a965465a8f0591ac15d10e7cb1bd4642","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下點先可以個別回復一個app既date？<br />\n因為我唔小心del左個i safe pro, 重裝之後無哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d野仲係iclould度 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣冇得搞<br />\nicloud drive isafe呢個位唔係for你咁用<br />\n佢唔係用嚟記app data, 應該for放文件之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你平時有冇做icloud backup<br />\n成部嘢restore一次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有做，上一次備份係3日前，我都諗緊呢個方法，但屋企個wifi神神， 成部restore 成100g 唔知要搞幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得用4g 讀返d data出黎？"},{"pid":"ee64265235b9aa4e1167e96e4ed5f38e9087210e","tid":389303,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下點先可以個別回復一個app既date？<br />\n因為我唔小心del左個i safe pro, 重裝之後無哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d野仲係iclould度 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣冇得搞<br />\nicloud drive isafe呢個位唔係for你咁用<br />\n佢唔係用嚟記app data, 應該for放文件之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你平時有冇做icloud backup<br />\n成部嘢restore一次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有做，上一次備份係3日前，我都諗緊呢個方法，但屋企個wifi神神， 成部restore 成100g 唔知要搞幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得用4g 讀返d data出黎？</blockquote><br />\n最緊要停咗個backup佢先，唔係一陣佢同你replace咗delete後嘅狀態<br />\n好似要wifi先得？4g你無限data？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727299c0e09b1d58668c3658b3868930644caa74","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你開咗個權限出嚟佢唔一定有save<br />\n同埋呢個位係做file management<br />\n你上面堆apps嘅app data唔會呢個位見到<br />\n去&quot;一般&gt;icloud用量&quot;睇就一清二楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下點先可以個別回復一個app既date？<br />\n因為我唔小心del左個i safe pro, 重裝之後無哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d野仲係iclould度 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣冇得搞<br />\nicloud drive isafe呢個位唔係for你咁用<br />\n佢唔係用嚟記app data, 應該for放文件之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你平時有冇做icloud backup<br />\n成部嘢restore一次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有做，上一次備份係3日前，我都諗緊呢個方法，但屋企個wifi神神， 成部restore 成100g 唔知要搞幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得用4g 讀返d data出黎？</blockquote><br />\n最緊要停咗個backup佢先，唔係一陣佢同你replace咗delete後嘅狀態<br />\n好似要wifi先得？4g你無限data？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyes, smt 無限 好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，平時極少會轉wifi 所以唔驚replace左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766b92666cb7621069ec8c9e13f9cf12ca496ecb","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"btw 唔該哂睇腸巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c56a46a0e59bb702c34bfaf50cad4fe2ea5ca56","tid":389303,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 唔該哂腸弟*巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}